query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(dd i inv ss) */ select i.i_item_id,
i.i_item_desc,
i.i_current_price
from inventory AS inv
inner join item AS i
on inv.inv_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND inv.inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500 AND i.i_current_price BETWEEN 30 AND 30 + 30 AND i.i_manufact_id IN (437,
129,
727,
663)
inner join date_dim AS dd
on dd.d_date_sk = inv.inv_date_sk AND dd.d_date BETWEEN '2002-05-30'::date AND '2002-07-29'::date
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk group by i.i_item_id, i.i_item_desc, i.i_current_price order by i.i_item_id LIMIT 100;
